					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The C standard specifies only the behavior of a conforming program. The compiler may produce any executable with that behavior. If a compiler wants to encode the data segment with RLE to store zero-filled arrays more efficiently, and then include startup code that decompresses the data segment, let it.</div>

